OL,3,CBook of LFC Stories compiles the work
OL,4,Cof Liverpool journalist for charity
OL,6,FThe stories of a Hillsborough
OL,7,Fcampaigner and journalist have been
OL,8,Fcompiled into a new book which has
OL,9,Fbeen published two years after his
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FDan Kay reported on Liverpool Football
OL,13,FClub for more than two decades before
OL,14,Fhe died in 2023.
OL,16,FThe book LFC Stories - Fascinating
OL,17,FTales From Liverpool's Incredible
OL,18,FHistory features his interviews and
OL,19,Freports, with proceeds going to a
OL,20,Fcharitable foundation set up in his
OL,21,Fmemory.
