OL,3,CBook of LFC Stories compiles the work
OL,4,Cof Liverpool journalist for charity
OL,6,FThe articles were curated by Dan's
OL,7,Fcolleague and former ECHO journalist
OL,8,FSam Carroll, with a foreword by
OL,9,FAnfield legend Sir Kenny Dalglish.
OL,11,FDan was known in Liverpool and the
OL,12,Fwider region for his journalism and
OL,13,Fcampaigning for Hillsborough justice.
OL,15,FHe died in May 2023 at the age of 45,
OL,16,Fwith his death prompting a huge
OL,17,Foutpouring of sadness and love from
OL,18,Fhis family, many friends and former
OL,19,Fcolleagues.
