OL,3,CBook of LFC Stories compiles the work
OL,4,Cof Liverpool journalist for charity
OL,6,FDan's editor at the Liverpool Echo,
OL,7,FMaria Breslin, said: "Dan's
OL,8,Fachievements and legacy were honoured
OL,9,Fwith a tribute in Parliament, a
OL,10,Fposthumous doctorate at Liverpool Hope
OL,11,FUniversity and the creation of new
OL,12,Fcharity - The Dan Kay Foundation.
OL,14,F"He often donated his time to
OL,15,Fcharities and good causes across the
OL,16,FNorth West and the charity aims to
OL,17,Fcontinue his legacy while tackling
OL,18,Fstigma around mental health and
OL,19,Fsuicide and spreading kindness."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
