OL,3,CBook of LFC Stories compiles the work
OL,4,Cof Liverpool journalist for charity
OL,6,FDan's cousin Amos, chair of the Dan
OL,7,FKay Foundation, said: "The book launch
OL,8,Fwas a huge moment for us and one that
OL,9,FDan would have been rightly proud of.
OL,10,FWe at the Dan Kay Foundation are too.
OL,12,F"A collection of Dan's writing at its
OL,13,Ffinest, it showcases many of his
OL,14,Ffinest attributes. His analysis,
OL,15,Fattention to detail, his loyalty,
OL,16,Fintegrity, generosity, empathy,
OL,17,Fencyclopaedic knowledge and his
OL,18,Fstorytelling. And the foreword was
OL,19,Fwritten by Dan's footballing idol Sir
OL,20,FKenny Dalglish."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
