OL,6,FThe book launch was sponsored by
OL,7,FDoughty Street Chambers and law firm
OL,8,FLeigh Day. The practice's human rights
OL,9,Fpartner Leanne Devine worked alongside
OL,10,FDan during the Hillsborough inquests
OL,11,Fwhere she represented families.
OL,13,FShe also represented Dan's family
OL,14,Fduring the inquest into his death.
