OL,3,CBook of LFC Stories compiles the work
OL,4,Cof Liverpool journalist for charity
OL,6,FLeanne said: "As someone who knew Dan
OL,7,Fthrough his work in covering many
OL,8,Fsocial justice issues in the city, I
OL,9,Fam extremely proud to be part of the
OL,10,FDan Kay Foundation, and that Leigh Day
OL,11,Fcan help sponsor the Foundation's
OL,12,Fevent to launch Dan's book.
OL,14,F"In addition to fundraising to support
OL,15,Flocal causes, the Dan Kay Foundation
OL,16,Faims to drive forward improvements to
OL,17,Four mental health services across the
OL,18,Fregion.
